title: Everybody Wants To Go To Heaven, But Nobody Wants to Die, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO246
itunes:title: Everybody Wants To Go To Heaven, But Nobody Wants to Die, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO246
description: Most people who want to be millionaires don't see the connection between today & someday. Young kids don't think that killing it at their job at Burger King has anything to do with making millions in the future. Adults don't think how they cut their grass or wipe their @ss has anything to do with achieving their "dream life." The people who *actually* become wealthy are different. They recognize the link between now & later & they make every effort & sacrifice RIGHT NOW. They die to live the good life
